  <exercise>
  <p>
    An object of height 1 cm is located at a distance 20 cm in front of a concave mirror of 
    focal length 10 cm. 
    <ol marker="a.">
      <li>
        What is the radius of curvature of the mirror?
      </li>
      <li>
        Where is the image located?
      </li>
      <li>
        Is the image real or virtual?
      </li>
      <li>
        What is the magnification of the mirror?
      </li>
      <li>
        Is the image enlarged or reduced?
      </li>
      <li>
        What is the height of the image?
      </li>
      <li>
        Is the image erect or inverted?
      </li>
    </ol>
     </p>
  </exercise>

